2. Standard charger means a charger employing a household type 13A socket. Medium charger means a charger with rated power of or below 20kW. Quick charger means charger with rated power above 20 kW.
標準充電器指採用家用型13A插座的充電器；中速充電器是指額定功率在20千瓦或以下的充電器；快速充電器是指額定功率大於20千瓦的充電器。

3. In general, a charger has either one socket or carries one charging cable except the following configurations:
除下列類型外，充電器一般有一個插頭或一條充電電缐：
